  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "construction General Forman",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Advertisement: General Foreman / Construction Site Supervisor</strong></h3><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore<br /><strong>Industry:</strong> Construction<br /><strong>Position:</strong> General Foreman / Site Supervisor</p><p>We are looking for a <strong>highly committed and experienced General Foreman / Construction Site Supervisor</strong> to manage site operations and lead workers effectively. This role requires <strong>hard work, long hours, and strong site discipline</strong>.</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Supervise daily construction activities and site workers</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with engineers, main contractor, subcontractors, and workers</p></li><li><p>Ensure work is carried out according to drawings, schedule, and safety requirements</p></li><li><p>Manage manpower, tools, and materials on site</p></li><li><p>Conduct toolbox meetings and ensure compliance with WSH regulations</p></li><li><p>Work at height and oversee high-risk activities</p></li><li><p>Handle <strong>day & night rotating shifts</strong> and <strong>overtime when required</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>3–5 years experience</strong> in construction site supervision</p></li><li><p>Strong leadership and ability to manage workers firmly</p></li><li><p>Willing to work <strong>long hours, overtime, weekends, and night shifts</strong></p></li><li><p>Able to work <strong>at height</strong> and in demanding site conditions</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of construction safety practices and MOM regulations</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills (English / Tamil / Hindi / basic Chinese preferred)</p></li><li><p>BCA Safety Supervisor Certificate / relevant construction certification is an advantage</p></li></ul><p><strong>Other Details</strong></p><ul><li><p>Physically fit and mentally strong</p></li><li><p>Able to handle pressure and tight schedules</p></li><li><p>Responsible, disciplined, and committed to work</p></li></ul><p><strong>Salary:</strong> Commensurate with experience<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> As per site requirement</p>",
